    <h1>Ad Fatigue</h1>
    <p class="description">The decline in ad performance that happens when your audience sees the same creative too many times. Performance drops by an average of <strong>45%</strong> once the same viewer has seen an ad more than 4 times.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
